490
01:00:02,182 --> 01:00:03,684
I have a degree in criminology.

491
01:00:03,850 --> 01:00:08,151
I've taken my fair share
of forensic science courses.

492
01:00:08,313 --> 01:00:13,570
I also know a series of connected
