667
01:18:35,502 --> 01:18:39,006
Oh, that is so sick!
God. you think that makes a difference?

668
01:18:39,173 --> 01:18:41,471
- It does.
- No, Ellison. It doesn't.

669
01:18:41,634 --> 01:18:43,682
You have done
some crazy shit in the past.

