676
01:19:00,027 --> 01:19:01,074
Yes.

677
01:19:01,237 --> 01:19:05,788
The previous owners of this home
were hung from a tree in our backyard?

678
01:19:05,950 --> 01:19:08,419
- Yes.
- That is so sick. Ellison.

